Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(762,282)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.01,0:01:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  可以不用削蟹黄堡的皮的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, you don't need to cut the crust off the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是在做快餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are making fast food
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱要慢慢来  乖儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love takes time, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.48,0:01:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把番茄给我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now hand me a tomato
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来把它雕成玫瑰装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can carve it into a rose garnish
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.98,0:01:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in blue blazes is going on in--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵太太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mrs. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hello, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在学做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:38.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm learning how to make Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How lovely
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能借用一下你儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I borrow your son for just a moment?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is going on here, boy-o?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈怎么会在厨房里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is your mother in the kitchen?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看外面的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take a look at that crowd
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我以后再也不出来堂食了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is why I never go out to eat anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你妈不关我蟹堡王的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your mommy has no business at my business
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送她回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send her home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,官方员工日历上面写着今天是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the official employee calendar says it's
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带妈妈上班日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring Your Mom to Work Day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(534,768)}妈妈日
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在是太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, that would have been awful
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.23,0:02:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到我妈一来会出啥乱就让我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It shivers me timbers to think
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what a disaster my mom would make if she was here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把你们的妈也请来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I invited your moms too
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.95,0:02:24.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:24.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真贴心啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful of you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就别闹了  给我看看你办的正事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so stop your horseplay and show me what you do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  你把我脸都丢光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother, you're embarrassing me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是在笑什么  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're chuckling about, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放眼望去全都是在浪费钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's wasted money everywhere I look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上次换炸锅里的油是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When was the last time you changed the oil in this fryer?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天都换
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We change it every day, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waste
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能一年一换
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should be but once a year
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用真番茄做的番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real tomato ketchup
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waste
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你厕所里的厕纸肯定是双层的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet in your latrine you use two-ply toilet paper
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只用单层的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We use one-ply
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞得跟纸是树上长的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As if it grows on trees
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waste
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该得用半层的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It should be half-ply
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,利润要想节节攀升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your profits would be much higher
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不准花钱大手大脚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you stopped spending willy-nilly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了要多笑  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember to smile, son
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my food?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉耽搁了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the delay, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的餐马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your order will be up soon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没要你不鄙视客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't say lose your disdain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且也别瘫着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't slouch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会伤到脊椎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin your spine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是无脊椎动物  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an invertebrate, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no back talk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这鄙视就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice disdain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但给客人鄙视就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But save it for the customers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老头简金斯的餐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up for Old Man Jenkins
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.30,0:04:02.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份去皮蟹黄堡  加一份配菜沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:02.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty with crust removed and one side salad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我点的是薯条  不是沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:05.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ordered fries, not a salad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,薯条就在沙拉里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fries are in the salad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯只是饿了才勉强吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But only 'cause I'm so hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想起了我妈在我小时候的厨艺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of my mother's cooking when I was but a boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梦回童年让我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm filled with childish glee
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的餐我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made everyone's orders
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈不懂快餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mom doesn't understand fast food--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not the way I do
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她做蟹黄堡要做大半天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her cooking takes forever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为她在里面加了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because she adds love
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.47,0:04:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这个蟹黄堡里没有爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean there's no love in this Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我只能吃出来快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all I taste is the fast
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要求退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I demand a refund
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我一点爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me some love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:58.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1472,240)}退钱
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There'll be no refunds
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里面可是有爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:04.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, there is love here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对你们钱的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My love for your money
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们应该不会拆散我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want to break us up, do ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把钱还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me my money back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:16.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478,814)}要爱餐\N不要快餐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the love?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们儿子很明显上班不用功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clearly, our sons aren't working hard enough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.01,0:05:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我的话  最失望的明明就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Believe me when I say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one is more disappointed than we
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,their mothers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为我们教导有方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We thought we taught them better
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了避免大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To avert this disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要接手蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're going to take over the restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我们儿子做正确的示范
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and show our boys how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:38.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.06,0:05:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zip it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们三个去羞羞脸墙角面壁思过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to the shame corner with you three
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,136)}羞羞脸墙角
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来把这里打理干净吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now time to spruce this place up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,776)}妈妈王\N家常菜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈王家常菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Mama Krabs Home-style Cooking"?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会出大乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be a disaster
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看她们对我蟹堡王怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at what they did to me restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里看着很有家的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the place looks homey
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真想要家的感觉  还不如待家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I wanted "homey," I'd stay at home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她们这样会花掉我不少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is costing me a fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵太太早就把这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mrs. SquarePants had all this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都放她船的后备箱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the trunk of her boat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好妈妈有备无患
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:13.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A mother is always prepared
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们几家的妈到最后肯定都会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eventually, our moms will crash and burn
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我们就夺回蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then we'll reclaim the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来马上就能夺回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's gonna happen sooner than later
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look who just arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个妈妈的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every mom's nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海海  你把娃娃落在船上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubby, you forgot your doll on the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是手办  不是娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an action figure, not a doll
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临妈妈王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Mama Krabs'
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right this way
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你们的菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your menus
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Interesting
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We shall see
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新来的老板能不能遭得住我挑三拣四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if this new management can stand up to my scrutiny
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我全都来一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will have one of every--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩都来一份早间特餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll both have the early-bird special
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  我要去打汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother, I'm going to get a soda
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水的吸管很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soda straws are dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,容易把眼睛戳出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll put your eye out
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换用这个喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Use this instead
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so embarrassing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两份蟹黄煲菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two Krabby Patty casseroles
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,切成小块  可以一口一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even cut it into bite-sized pieces
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家儿子就喜欢这么吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just how my boy likes it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个妈宝男果然喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course that mama's boy would like it here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, look
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.49,0:07:53.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好像都很喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:53.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone is liking it here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,210)}甜蜜的家
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脸上有点脏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got some smudge
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,664)}小费
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Danke
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're a success
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, of course they are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看她们干活多卖力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look how hard they're working
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看咱妈干活  感觉心里很不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I actually feel kind of guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,seeing them do all the work
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How pathetic
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们三个很明显不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You three clearly don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.18,0:08:25.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么领略母亲的溺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how to appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:25.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the smothering embrace of motherly love
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你有什么意见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王有地下室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are these premises equipped with a basement?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.07,0:08:43.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位  隆重介绍成年子女孤堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, I present
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the fortress of solitude for adult children
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是个堆满垃圾的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a junk-filled basement
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看到的是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see junk
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是休闲大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hangout lounge
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Correct
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总比羞羞脸墙角强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better than the shame corner
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.77,0:09:04.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这可以爱咋打发时间就咋打发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down here, you can spend your time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,doing whatever you want
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看漫画  打电玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reading comics, playing video games
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上网瞎骂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,complaining on the Internet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的生活选择太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your life choices are lame
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过总体概念我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I like the overall concept
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你们妈就在楼上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And with your mother upstairs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,点心随叫随到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,snacks are just a holler away
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我妈就爱做点心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mom loves to make snacks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还有什么要传授的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What else can you teach us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很会偷懒的智者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,oh wise sage of the slacker ways?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜我马上就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, my time with you is at an end
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都很乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have been a good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我妈要带我去吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my mother is taking me for ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒计时三二一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in three, two, one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好去吃冰淇淋了  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready for my ice cream, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,姐妹再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, girls
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎下次再来  听见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back soon, you hear
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来可以试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we can give it a try
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mo-om
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  玉米片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, nachos
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch the fort
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.59,0:10:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ma
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.98,0:10:32.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:32.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Mommy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来都没睡得这么香过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never slept better in me life
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,昨晚有种梦回童年的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Last night made me feel like a kid again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.16,0:10:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这就是童年的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's what it's like to have a childhood
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们是我这位小朋友最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are the best buddies a kid could ever have
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈  早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom, breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉哪里不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, I think something's wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Agreed, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We better go check
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Booyah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这群懒鬼都谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are these bums?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来了啊  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.45,0:11:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我做个你一直说的那个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go fix me one of those Krabbity Patties
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're always going on about
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是带爸爸上班日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today is Bring Your Dad to Work Day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1340,792)}爸爸日
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿子  可不可以顺带帮我续个杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While you're up, son, could you refill my drink?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我再来点薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And more chips for me, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡做好就叫我  儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any time you're ready with that Krabbity Patty, son
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.09,0:11:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my mommy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.69,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&}宠物石头
