Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:57.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(648,886)}宠物公园
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你今天能来宠物公园  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you can come to the pet park today, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for inviting me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要看小蜗新学的魔术了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see Gary's new tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.75,0:12:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带宠物来宠物公园最好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more fun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than bringing your pet to a pet park
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.35,0:12:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑袋里有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got one of those head things
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脑震荡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A concussion?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.23,0:12:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还有另外一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But also the other thing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:35.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A thought
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我想带我自己的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I'd like to have my own pet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到宠物公园玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to bring to the pet park
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这想法就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就到路边的宠物店看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can stop at the pet store on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1164,472)}宠物店
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有没有你喜欢的宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do any of these pets pique your fancy?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.88,0:13:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want that one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个宠物适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the pet for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,384)}宠物公园
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, go on through
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你提供宠物证明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need to see some proof of pet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a rock
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名字叫滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His name is Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来这哪算宠物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see how this thing is a pet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.16,0:13:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凑近一点看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take a closer look
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:35.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's adorable
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go right in
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就是我的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's my card
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开采晶洞  趣味多多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Geode hunting is a cracking good time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水晶石英晶格完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The perfect crystal quartz lattice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的收藏增添了一份精致的标本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An exquisite specimen for my collection
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚  你是最棒的石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly, you're the best rock ever
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the devil?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By Jove
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甚是壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Such majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面的晶洞肯定不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must have quite the geode inside
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tallyho, good chap
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珀西弗尔采石家  业余晶洞爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perciful Rockhound, amateur geode enthusiast
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你讲话好搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You talk funny
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, Rolly?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚想要跟你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly says he wants to play with you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们两个玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun, you two
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Rolly?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.79,0:15:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它在跟那边那位搞笑八字胡老头玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's playing with the funny mustache man over there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So cute
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过也玩差不多了  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's enough play, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天想跟大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want to play with everyone today
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Done already?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是乖石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  也许得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, maybe we should leave
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行啊  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正大家都睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody here is sleeping anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要敲开那颗石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will tear that rock asunder
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fun day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在就来做我最爱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time to do my favorite thing--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.73,0:16:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海胆哥与败蜗子秀  开播
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the "Sir Urchin & Snail Fail Show"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,404)}海胆哥与败蜗子秀
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'd I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SquarePants residence
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚好像不喜欢电视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think Rolly likes TV
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它把家都拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He tore up the place
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有喂过它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been feeding him?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物没东西吃容易发飙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets get cranky if they don't get their food
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1288,898)}滚滚
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝说你得吃不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob said you need lots of food
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.91,0:17:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我手上有这一大袋水泥综合点心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I had this big bag of cement mix on hand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1028,428)}水泥
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加水即可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just add water
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.34,0:17:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用餐愉慢  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bone apple teeth, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我得来吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for my lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢干吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like it dry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚  你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly, you got big
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喂了滚滚  它就长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I fed Rolly, and he got big
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它是要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he dying?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you silly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它可能是想去外面遛遛  上个厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He probably just needs a walk to go potty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过遛它一定要牵绳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But make sure he wears his leash
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该去遛遛了  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for a walk, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界都是你的马桶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The world is your toilet
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My word
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的石头长得好圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How rotund his rock has grown
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要偷到那颗圆滚滚的石子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must pilfer that plump pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥味道这么臭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What stinks?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你啊  滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you, Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该干什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚有股垃圾馊水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly smells like garbage water
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是对我发火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he mad at me?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course not
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以带去宠物美容店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can take him to a groomer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to freshen him up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:56.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1338,218)}便利\N石头美容店
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便利石头美容店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Conveniently Placed Rock Groomer
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边就有一家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one right here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是石头美容师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the rock groomer
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我那颗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.29,0:19:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收藏价值极高的耀眼巨石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ample, glorious collectible rock from you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚得洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly needs a bath
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At last
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.52,0:19:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你坚固外表下的闪耀内心就要归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the glimmering contents
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of your sturdy aspects shall be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:42.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后  你这怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back, you beast
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finished already?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚  你好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly, you're beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得跟海绵宝宝说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta tell SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又打来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  滚滚已经美得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Rolly looks prettier than
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比特别美的东西还美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a really pretty thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定得来看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gotta see him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就该带它参加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you should bring him down
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村宠物秀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:11.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Bikini Bottom Pet Show
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟小蜗现在就在现场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary and I are here now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:15.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,422)}裤头村宠物秀
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不见不散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐  你得洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady, you need a bath
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(922,244)}裤头村宠物秀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,700)}牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,24号参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Contestant 24
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它就叫滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His name is Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he pretty?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它有什么才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does it do?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表演给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Patrick, go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Patrick, go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta-da
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来其他参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems every other contestant
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都被淘汰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been eliminated
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}消 灭
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也只能当你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suppose you win
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是默认的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by default
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,810)}宠物冠军
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,did it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚  你是最棒的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly, you're the best rock--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ever
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蕴藏在里面的水晶珍宝总算归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, your crystalline cache is all mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真棒  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-g-good show, old chap
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, fiddlesticks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚滚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rolly
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱你的新模样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love your new look
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.07,0:22:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来滚滚从头到尾都是颗蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So Rolly was an egg all along
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that's what I call a pet
